oda-data-set.name: LogDS
oda-data-set.xml-property: select batch_rev_no, be_seq_no, task_name, obj_exec_start_time, obj_exec_end_time, decode(status, 'CO', 'Completed', '99', 'Failed', 'SP', 'Suspended', 'UC', 'Under Consideration', 'PC', 'Pro-Created', 'Unknown') as status, pre_post, error_description from log where batch_no = ? and status <> 'CO' order by be_seq_no

oda-data-set.name: BatchDS
oda-data-set.xml-property: select * from batch where batch_no = ? --and batch_rev_no = ?

oda-data-set.name: FailedObjectsDS
oda-data-set.xml-property: select object_name as task_name, count(1) graph_value from log where batch_no = ? and status = ? group by object_name order by object_name

oda-data-set.name: InstructionParametersDS
oda-data-set.xml-property: select a.* from instruction_parameters a, batch b where a.instruction_log_no = b.instruction_seq_no and a.name not in ( select code3 from configuration where code1 = 'CORE' and code2 = 'DEL_INSTR_PARAMS' ) and b.batch_no = ?

oda-data-set.name: BatchJobStatisticsDS
oda-data-set.xml-property: select decode(status, 'CO', 'Completed', '99', 'Failed', 'SP', 'Suspended', 'UC', 'Under Consideration', 'PC', 'Pro-Created', 'Unknown') as status, count(1) cnt from log where batch_no = ? group by status order by status

oda-data-set.name: PrePostJobsDS
oda-data-set.xml-property: select pre_post, object_name, decode(status, 'CO', 'Completed', '99', 'Failed', 'SP', 'Suspended', 'UC', 'Under Consideration', 'PC', 'Pro-Created', 'Unknown') as status, count(1) cnt from log where batch_no = ? and pre_post in ('PRE', 'POST') group by pre_post, object_name, status order by pre_post, object_name, status

oda-data-set.name: ProgressLevelDS
oda-data-set.xml-property: select batch_rev_no, cycle_no, prg_level_type, prg_activity_type, start_datetime, end_datetime, failed_over from progress_level where batch_no = ? order by start_datetime

oda-data-set.name: ExecutionOrderDS
oda-data-set.xml-property: select distinct entity, precedence_order from column_map order by precedence_order
